88811,"uid":147376,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T13:26:15.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">雖然佢辭咗職但接手嗰個都係紅到仆街</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rH4qkX0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrH4qkX0.jpg&h=f4f24e2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有傳媒報道，去年因公開撐警而令香港吉野家捲入罷食、「裝修」風波的合興集團行政總裁洪明基，於5月13日，辭任吉野家快餐（香港）董事，由合興集團旗下北京吉野家快餐高層<strong><span class=\"red\">郭培廉</span></strong>接任。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T13:33:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2rAw0ZP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2rAw0ZP.jpg&h=63d8fbf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你嗰個文宣唔啱㗎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Uwszky.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Uwszky.png&h=49cd0aca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1331979840203030/posts/2405218406212496/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1331979840203030%2Fposts%2F2405218406212496%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1Tvbkzvns01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=e1f493c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1331979840203030/posts/2405218406212496/?d=n</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T13:58:42.000Z","msg":"圖冇駱駝牌"},{"pid":"e78a941388a32098746b9b6c905f2226c276c93c","tid":2488811,"uid":126100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0117c374636d50b432d931a1d362eff722813b03","tid":2488811,"uid":32699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5948bf775f2d2643242fefa7fe98ac917b24106f","tid":2488811,"uid":257231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5a59da0a8714d5c0a9bb002b4d6663573c99caca","tid":2488811,"uid":222907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T13:39:00.000Z","msg":"調撚左味"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T13:53:32.000Z","msg":"條撚準未"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T13:55:46.000Z","msg":"搖撚準備"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T13:59:01.000Z","msg":"唔撚準避"},{"pid":"d2ac130417f98ee82c4533a42c72cab805c48585","tid":2488811,"uid":319512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eae6cf3d4aff13182025fb6a1413efda09f44b62","tid":2488811,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T13:07:22.000Z","msg":"這家來自日本的快餐連鎖品牌近日公佈了2020年財報。報告顯示，吉野家2020財年營業額同比下滑超20%，淨虧損高達75億日元（約合4.5億元人民幣）。<br />\n<br />\n據瞭解，吉野家目前在全球擁有超1000家海外門店，其中中國門店佔六成以上。不過在去年，為降低成本，吉野家宣佈在今年2月前關閉全球150家店鋪，其中中國門店50家。<br />\n<br />\n新冠疫情發生以來，吉野家更是計劃在日本推出專營外賣服務。<br />\n<br />\n企查查APP顯示， 吉野家（中國）投資有限公司成立於2015年6月，法定代表人為安井昭裕，註冊資本為4800萬美元。事實上，中國吉野家門店背後，其實有兩個運營主體，一個是日本吉野家，另一個是香港上市公司合興集團。合興集團憑借與日本吉野家簽署的長期特許協議，在中國北方運營吉野家。<br />\n<br />\n有觀點認為，吉野家之所以能在日本屹立百年不倒，除了味道獨特之外，還在於其便宜。至於名字來源並非創始人叫吉野，而是地名吉野山。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T13:59:08.000Z","msg":"bye <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83de6662c124f945516a1d2f07def7b87092528d","tid":2488811,"uid":252541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3119a7bbb93ba770697c74509d73b4024877d93a","tid":2488811,"uid":71266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbe6c39d7a4751ecd509ab8d341c72e080fcac90","tid":2488811,"uid":252541,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9951fb8747907e717a7c3b65d472127faf9414a5","tid":2488811,"uid":147376,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T13:26:15.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">雖然佢辭咗職但接手嗰個都係紅到仆街</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rH4qkX0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrH4qkX0.jpg&h=f4f24e2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有傳媒報道，去年因公開撐警而令香港吉野家捲入罷食、「裝修」風波的合興集團行政總裁洪明基，於5月13日，辭任吉野家快餐（香港）董事，由合興集團旗下北京吉野家快餐高層<strong><span class=\"red\">郭培廉</span></strong>接任。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T13:33:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2rAw0ZP.